elements.text: small update but I think the idea may be interesting to some:

text: The core idea is that there's no special ui for stuff like the about page and open source licenses page, they are all presented as data and as such, they can be used like any other thing in the application (in the video I create a chart aggregating the dependencies by license type), I also show the introduction of the link data type as a core type and two new functions that operate on the new type (get link title and get link address)
